reviewText: One of the better actors of our time and in a series of great stories!!

Four top notch films that star the great Denzel Washington.  Bought this for less than $10 and it was well worth it.  Three of the four films he stars alongside some other heavy hitters like Russell Crowe in "American Gangster", Angelina Jolie in "The Bone Collector", and Jodie Foster in "Inside Man".  Great set and great movies.
